.cx%2Fi%2Fpyrcfjq.gif&amp;h=9f6bf1e8&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<br />\nTrello 開左Public美股認真討論區 board，慢慢搬野上去。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://trello.com/b/513A9wIT\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftrello.com%2Fb%2F513A9wIT&d=90j3dNidiaWpDV5wjwn%2B65nDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=6cd10c8f\" target=\"_blank\">https://trello.com/b/513A9wIT</a><br />\n<br />\n開左個美股認真討論區（全民編輯留言區），巴打可以加野上去，周末有空會整理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://trello.com/b/1SNId2E3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftrello.com%2Fb%2F1SNId2E3&d=90j3dNidiaWpDV5wjwn%2B65nDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=302375d0\" target=\"_blank\">https://trello.com/b/1SNId2E3</a><br />\n<br />\n記得用假名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://temp-mail.org/en/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftemp-mail.org%2Fen%2F&d=90j3dNidiaWpDV5wjwn%2B65nDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=cdfc9a02\" target=\"_blank\">https://temp-mail.org/en/</a><br />\n<br />\n記得要加左下面條link member先可以留言<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://trello.com/invite/b/1SNId2E3/b3210a9ad8d0743204ac005aef0d25d5/%E7%BE%8E%E8%82%A1%E8%AA%8D%E7%9C%9F%E8%A8%8E%E8%AB%96%E5%8D%80%EF%BC%88%E5%85%A8%E6%B0%91%E7%B7%A8%E8%BC%AF%E7%95%99%E8%A8%80%E5%8D%80%EF%BC%89\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftrello.com%2Finvite%2Fb%2F1SNId2E3%2Fb3210a9ad8d0743204ac005aef0d25d5%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E8%2582%25A1%25E8%25AA%258D%25E7%259C%259F%25E8%25A8%258E%25E8%25AB%2596%25E5%258D%2580%25EF%25BC%2588%25E5%2585%25A8%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%25B7%25A8%25E8%25BC%25AF%25E7%2595%2599%25E8%25A8%2580%25E5%258D%2580%25EF%25BC%2589&d=90j3dNidiaWpDV5wjwn%2B65nDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=37381500\" target=\"_blank\">https://trello.com/invite/